
---

**APIRollingLens**  
**Description:**  
Tracks performance changes across API endpoints with a rolling time window and visual pulse overlays.

```markdown
# APIRollingLens - Time-Sensitive API Performance Viewer

APIRollingLens continuously scans endpoints and highlights degradation or delay within a dynamic rolling window.

## Features
- Time-window-based tracking  
- Overlay charts for latency  
- JSON / CSV logging

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/APIRollingLens.git
cd APIRollingLens
python monitor.py
